*Drugar*ice su mi uvek tu da me podrže. (My friends are always there to support me.)

Uvek ću imati *drugara* i nikada neću ostati sam. (I will always have a friend and I will never be alone.)

*Drugar*i su nam najbolji kada nam je najteže. (Friends are the best for us when times are toughest.)

On je bio moj dobri *drugar*. (He was my good friend.)

Oni su bili najbolji *drugari*. (They were the best of friends.)